title-of-article: Pre-order Paper Mario: The Origami King from the Nintendo Official UK Store and receive a free Origami Sheet and Magnet Set
content:
If you pre-order Paper Mario: The Origami King from the Nintendo Official UK Store either physically or digitally you can get a free Origami Sheet and Magnet Set!

Discover more about the game at the Paper Mario: The Origami King website.
